"><u>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35514364/</u></span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9L3EDUCMV_text","label":"gg9L3EDUCMV_text","default":"Find Lasting Relief With SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager"},{"type":"html","id":"gg986IODh90_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg986IODh90_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f5b26110-2655-434f-8ff3-f12bd892c75b.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGQXnMY5zT_text","label":"ggGQXnMY5zT_text","default":"Find Lasting Relief With SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager"},{"type":"html","id":"ggihBBrHnWy_text","label":"ggihBBrHnWy_text","default":"<p><strong>The SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager is quickly becoming a go-to solution for people tired of living with back, neck, and muscle pain.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5A_s7vPft_text","label":"gg5A_s7vPft_text","default":"<p>After just a few uses, you can expect to feel muscles loosen, tension fade, and a renewed sense of energy.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3GwCpV-GT_text","label":"gg3GwCpV-GT_text","default":"<p><strong>No more relying on painkillers to get through the day.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0znNmAU8T_text","label":"gg0znNmAU8T_text","default":"<p><strong>No more stiffness that limits how you move or how you live.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOLny2Lf9H_text","label":"ggOLny2Lf9H_text","default":"<p><strong>No more costly therapy appointments eating up your time and money.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYhZQDCRPW_text","label":"ggYhZQDCRPW_text","default":"<p>Just attach the SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager, set your intensity, and let it help your body heal - one 15-minute session at a time.</p>"}],
